room_title: Escape room "Shady Hills Vineyard" by Hill Country Escape in Fredericksburg (TX)
room_description: You and your friends are on a wine tour here in Hill Country, when y’all sneak away to investigate rumors of the winery’s success. You take a wrong turn and find yourself locked in the janitor’s closet! You have 60 minutes to ESCAPE back into the tasting room & meet back up with the group before anyone notices you’re missing!
